## Bazaarvoice Hosted UI Resources binaries

This page contains binaries for code in the [HostedUIResources](https://github.com/brentthomas/HostedUIResources) project.  Please see the project for documentation and additional details.

***

### Java SEO SDK Binaries

* 1.0 standalone JAR - [bvseosdk-1.0.jar](http://brentthomas.github.io/HostedUIResources/binaries/seosdk/java/1.0/bvseosdk-1.0.jar)
* 1.0 JAR with dependencies - [bvseosdk-1.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar](http://brentthomas.github.io/HostedUIResources/binaries/seosdk/java/1.0/bvseosdk-1.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
